Merely 4 years old in the U.S. market, e-commerce sales continue to grow on an annual basis. The purpose of this analysis is to test the significance of the rate of growth of e-commerce at TopHairWigs.com for 2014 to 2017. Especially, Beauty-Supplier type of ecommerce usually deals with a huge number of different kind of products so that it is hard to represent product on the mainpage efficiently. The data includes orders, products, and customers information. The forecast based on the significance of relation with sales, products and customers region will help increase sales rate and also choose targeting porducts on the mainpage more efficiently.
